MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

2010-1475. Middleton v. Meijer, Inc.

Montgomery App. No. 23789, 2010-Ohio-3244. This cause is pending before the court as a discretionary appeal. Upon consideration of appellant’s application for dismissal,

It is ordered by the court that the application for dismissal is granted. Accordingly, this cause is dismissed.
